title.narrative: MA-Regional Potable Water Supply Systems Project

description.narrative: The project development objective (PDO) is to increase access to potable water supply for selected communities in the project provinces of Nador, Driouch, Safi, Youssoufia, Sidi Bennour, and Errachidia.
